JEAN v2.0.0
Joint Epigenetic Analysis of Nanopore

JEAN is a comprehensive tool for analyzing epigenetic modifications from nanopore sequencing data. It combines direct methylation detection with computational prediction of lactylation and acetylation, followed by electrochemical simulation and advanced visualization.

Author: Ibrahim A. G. A. (amrgalalibrahim@gmail.com)

If you use please Cite: Amr Galal Abdelraheem Ibrahim, Edson Aparecido Adrano. JEAN: Joint Epigenetic Analysis of Nanopore pipeline for detecting methylation, acetylation, and lactylation. Authorea. October 26, 2025.
